CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 13, 1957, pg. 13 reads: "Daisy E. Lampkin Lauded for Service to Mankind At Colorful Testimonial in Webster Hall - Out-Of-Town Guests included Mrs. Lampkin's nieces, left, Reba Bowie and third from left, Gladys Bowie Duckett, Philadelphia; second from left, Fannie Howard, Baltimore."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three nieces of Daisy Lampkin, left to right: Reba Bowie, Fannie Howard, and Gladys Bowie Duckett, standing in Webster Hall for banquet
